Package dataAccess

Class UserAccessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • dataAccess.Accessor<User>
      • dataAccess.UserAccessor
  • public class UserAccessor
extends Accessor<User>
    A collection of methods that give access to User models in the database. It can create, delete, update, and find Users using a variety of methods.
